text: Muhammad Anwaarul Haq (born 1 January 1957) is a Pakistani jurist and 47th Chief Justice of Lahore High Court. ==Career== Haq was appointed as justice of Lahore High Court on 19 February 2010. He became chief justice of the same court on 22 October 2018. ==References== Category:1957 births Category:Living people Category:Judges of the Lahore High Court Category:Pakistani judges
